*.aar
*.dex
*.class

# Xcode & iOS Build Outputs
ios/build/
**/ios/build/
ios/build_device/
**/build_device/
ios/DerivedData/
**/DerivedData/
**/*.xcworkspace/
**/*.xcuserstate
**/*.xcuserdatad
**/*.xcresult/
